# Security Policy

## Supported Versions
This project is in pre-prototype stage (Patent Pending). Only the latest commit is supported.

## Reporting a Vulnerability
If you discover a security issue (especially anything related to data handling or alerts), please report it privately to:
patricia.sanford [at] your-email.com

Do **not** open a public GitHub issue.

We will respond within 48 hours and work with you on responsible disclosure.

Thank you for helping keep WallyGuard secure for vulnerable users.
